sellerCard.description:
This is Salam Sheikh, I’m a Young Front End Web Developer.

Here at Fiverr, I am offering my service on work related to frontend web development. High attention to detail and being punctual are my specialty. I always focus on building long-term relationships with all my clients by delivering the work as requested at a competitive price.
If you have any queries, please reach out to me and I’ll be more than happy to answer them.

description.content:
Hi buddy,

Are you searching for a frontend web developer who can do your frontend project on time? then you have found the right gig.

I'm a Frontend Web Developer, I mastered React Js, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap. I can convert your design into pixel perfect frontend website. I provide well structured, cross-browse compatibility, valid, adaptive, featured, clean, readable and maintainable code.


My SERVICES:

  • PSD/Figma/XD/Sketch to HTML
  • PSD/Figma/XD/Sketch to React Website
  • A fully responsive Website (Frontend)
  • Redesign or recreate an existing website
  • Web Customization
  • Custom Design to Development using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap, React (optional)


What Ill need from you:

  • File or link to your design.
  • Instruction/requirements if any.


WHY ME?

  • Quick Turnaround
  • Fast and great communicating skills.
  • 100% Transparency and customer satisfaction.
  • Neat and Clean Source Code.
  • SEO-friendly codes.
  • Well Organized files.
  • Fast Delivery
  • Unlimited revisions till satisfaction
  • 24/7 availability


Cost And Time:

Cost and time depend on on-page and content. So it would be really appreciated if you contact me to discuss details before placing an order. 


Best Regards,

Salam Sheikh

questionsAndAnswers.question: What format do you need for converting a design into responsive pages?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: It can PSD, Figma, XD, Sketch, PNG, JPEG, PDF, etc. If you don't have any of these then you can simply give me the link to a similar website you want to create.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What will be the delivery time of the project?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Project Delivery time is mentioned in the gig, but these are the maximum time. I will try to complete your project as soon as possible.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you deploy my website to server after development?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will deploy the website to your server but we need to discuss about that because cost & time varies based on the nature of the website and the server/hosting.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What happens if I placed direct order without discussion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Don't worry, I will check your requirements and if those requirements fall in the package you ordered that it's completely fine I will work on it and deliver your task. But if the requirements don't match with the package you ordered we will discuss & add extra time & cost into the order

reviews.comment: Pretty disappointed with my website and doubt I will end up using it. Very rude and unpolite when asked simple questions, plenty of bugs that need fixing but I need to submit the order apparently. Stay clear

seller_response.comment: I'm not sure why you've added this review, I fixed every single thing you asked for, I don't mean to be rude, modifications are a part of the task, I always asked you what else we need! we can't make a perfect product without revisions. I also delivered the project before the deadline ends but still you are not satisfied, sorry about it.

reviews.comment: Pixel perfect website and delivered early. Did an exceptional job at bringing the designs to life. The pages are responsive and looks good on all screen types as requested. I am very happy with the value provided and I would work with him again.

I had a fantastic experience working with this seller! Their expertise in Next.js is truly impressive, delivering high-quality work with clean, efficient code. What stood out the most was their patience and professionalism throughout the process. They took the time to address my questions, made revisions without hesitation, and ensured everything met my expectations. Highly recommended for anyone looking for a skilled and polite developer. Will definitely work with them again!

seller_response.comment: I really appreciate your words, Thanks again

Md. Abdus Salam truly SHINES in website development, showcasing impeccable attention to detail and expert coding that FAR exceeded expectations. With proactive communication and a cooperative spirit, working with him was smooth and efficient. His fast responses, fluency in HTML/CSS, and excellent input make collaborations productive and enjoyable! 👍
